OL,3,CWoman who saved boy, 15, from drowning
OL,4,Cissues water safety warning
OL,6,FA woman who saved a 15-year-old boy
OL,7,Ffrom drowning said she "didn't even
OL,8,Fthink twice" about jumping into a
OL,9,Friver to save him, and is warning of
OL,10,Fthe dangers of open water swimming.
OL,12,FNatalie Wilson jumped into the River
OL,13,FNith in Dumfries to save the boy after
OL,14,Fshe saw him get into difficulty in the
OL,15,Fwater.
OL,17,FAfter getting into the river and
OL,18,Fmanaging to get hold of the boy, the
OL,19,F31-year-old found herself in
OL,20,Fdifficulty too. She told ITV Border:
OL,21,F"It was just awful.
