OL,6,F"The ground moved away from our feet,
OL,7,Fso that's when panic set in for both
OL,8,Fof us, and we were both submerging
OL,9,Funderneath the water."
OL,11,FAfter a struggle and panic, Natalie
OL,12,Fwas able to swim and drag the teenager
OL,13,Fto the edge of the river, where they
OL,14,Fwere pulled onto the stones by a group
OL,15,Fof boys nearby.
