OL,3,CWoman who saved boy, 15, from drowning
OL,4,Cissues water safety warning
OL,6,FThe Nith Inshore Rescue Service has
OL,7,Fsaid anyone who finds themselves in
OL,8,Fdifficulty in the water should try and
OL,9,Fremain calm.
OL,11,FThey also say people should not enter
OL,12,Fthe water in the event of an emergency
OL,13,Fand instead call 999, and ask for the
OL,14,Fcoastguard.
OL,16,FIt is also advised that people use
OL,17,Fsafety rings or material that could be
OL,18,Fused to help somebody to safety - like
OL,19,Flong branches or rope.
