OL,6,FThe 15-year-old boy was then taken to
OL,7,FDumfries and Galloway Royal Infirmary.
OL,8,FHis family has confirmed that tests
OL,9,Fshow he was starved of oxygen for a
OL,10,Fsignificant period of time, and he
OL,11,Fremains in a serious condition in
OL,12,Fhospital.
OL,14,FThe mother of the rescued teenager
OL,15,Fthanked the group of boys for helping,
OL,16,Fand said without Natalie, her son
OL,17,Fwouldn't be here.
