OL,3,CWoman who saved boy, 15, from drowning
OL,4,Cissues water safety warning
OL,6,FNatalie is calling for more signage to
OL,7,Fwarn people of the dangers around open
OL,8,Fwater - including by the River Nith -
OL,9,Fas well as swimming lessons in schools.
OL,11,FShe said: "There is a strong current,
OL,12,Fthere's not one sign around here, not
OL,13,Fa pole, nothing."
OL,15,FThe incident is the second open water
OL,16,Femergency this week, after a multi-
OL,17,Fagency response to a group of stranded
OL,18,Fteenagers who were rescued from the
OL,19,Fsea at Southerness.
